@toollean v0.1
@tool himalaya
@desc CLI to manage emails via IMAP/SMTP. Use `himalaya` to list, read, write, reply, forward, search, and organize emails from the terminal. Supports multiple accounts and message composition with MML (MIME Meta Language).
@source /app/skills/himalaya/SKILL.md
@example
  > himalaya account configure
